commit.message:
ghdlsynth: never display a foreign module as pure vhdl

(do not try to display the original entity when this is none)
Increase stack size to 8MB for msys2-mcode (fix ghdl/ghdl#1742)
synth: file renaming for decls, expr, insts and stmts.
synth: use a generic version of synth-environment.
Makefile.in: remove circular reference for ghwdump on Linux

testsuite/testenv.sh: Add ghw_dump function

Also define ghw_dump to have only one function that calls GHWDUMP.
testsuite: try to determine ghwdump location automatically
doc/development/building/LLVM: add 12.0 to the list of supported versions
